You can download this release from [http://www.openttd.org/en/download-stable/1.0.0 openttd.org].

==Major new features==

* [[en/Archive/Community/Sound Effects Replacement|Sound Replacement sets]]
* [[en/Archive/Community/Music replacement project|Music Replacements sets]]
* Fully scalable GUI and improved right-to-left language support {{en/Flyspray|1905}}
* Smallmap Zoom-out
* Founding towns in-game
* Possibility to add Rail Types
* Moving AIs in AI Config Window
* [[en/Archive/Manual/Shade windows|Shading of Windows]]
* [[en/Manual/Console#game-commands|Reconnect Console Command]]
* Non Automatic Screenshot names
* Station Foundation GRF Support
* Full IPv6 Support
* Tons of crash fixes

